#

Pork and Coleslaw Wraps

25 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickComfort Food

Description

Savory pulled pork wrapped in a crunchy coleslaw for a delightful and easy meal.

Ingredients

  • shredded pork: 2 cups
  • coleslaw mix: 2 cups
  • large flour tortillas: 4
  • bbq sauce: 1/2 cup
  • green onions: 2, chopped
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
